EventIntroSequence2.SourceString: Yeah, I have a bad feeling about this...
EventIntroSequence2.LocalizedString: Yeah, I have a bad feeling about this...

EventBossDefeated00.SourceString: You may have stopped me here, but ZERATH THE DEVOURER will give me more power!
EventBossDefeated00.LocalizedString: You may have stopped me here, but ZERATH THE DEVOURER will give me more power!

EventBossDefeated02.SourceString: This fight is over. I am taking your precious Drake!
EventBossDefeated02.LocalizedString: This fight is over. I am taking your precious Drake!

EventBossDefeated04.SourceString: We need you now more than ever, Breaker! Please allow one of us to join you on your journey.
EventBossDefeated04.LocalizedString: We need you now more than ever, Breaker! Please allow one of us to join you on your journey.

EventUsePowerUp.SourceString: His attacks are too powerful, I need to protect the team!
EventUsePowerUp.LocalizedString: His attacks are too powerful, I need to protect the team!

EventAttackAfterPowerUp.SourceString: Laric's Shield absorbed that attack and turned it into a Powerstrike. Unleash it on the enemy!
EventAttackAfterPowerUp.LocalizedString: Laric's Shield absorbed that attack and turned it into a Powerstrike. Unleash it on the enemy!

EventBossTaunt.SourceString: HA! Another group of PITIFUL warriors to add to our crystal collection!
EventBossTaunt.LocalizedString: HA! Another group of PITIFUL warriors to add to our crystal collection!

RazorSkillUse.SourceString: Pitiful, eh? We'll see who's pitiful when my shards of LIGHT chase you back to your SHADOWY abyss!
RazorSkillUse.LocalizedString: Pitiful, eh? We'll see who's pitiful when my shards of LIGHT chase you back to your SHADOWY abyss!

Event_Quiet.SourceString: Did you hear something?  This place is starting to give me the creeps...
Event_Quiet.LocalizedString: Did you hear something?  This place is starting to give me the creeps...

Event_Shrine.SourceString: Use that shrine to refill our mana.  I have a feeling we're going to need it soon...
Event_Shrine.LocalizedString: Use that shrine to refill our mana.  I have a feeling we're going to need it soon...
